node.text: Some sharp-eyed readers have already spotted these, but let’s make it official! 🥰 Select retailers in the US, UK, and Canada will have editions of House of Sky and Breath with exclusive bonus scenes. (A bunch of retailers also have listings for signed books, but you guys already grabbed them all! 🤣💖) If you missed out, keep watching – there will be more info coming this fall on how/where to pre-order a signed copy from some amazing Indie booksellers! #crescentcity #houseofskyandbreath #hosab

node.text:
Stunning Maui sunset felt like the perfect way to celebrate House of Sky and Breath being officially done!! Well, the writing and editing anyway. 😎 There’s still loads happening behind the scenes at my publisher, but this book is officially one step closer to being in your hands! 💖🌙💖
 
And I know some of you have already seen this online, so I’m confirming that yes, the on sale date is now February 15th, 2022! 
 
More details coming soon about signed books and exclusive editions! 🥰 

#houseofskyandbreath #crescentcity #hosab #maui #hawaii #sunset

node.text: SO EXCITED! ☺️💖☺️ @lynettenoni is one of my favorite people on the planet and I’m so honored to celebrate the release of her incredible new book! Link in bio for tickets (first 200 will get a signed bookplate from me)!! Hope to see you there!! #theprisonhealer #lynettenoni #events

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sarah J. Maas on March 26, 2021. May be an image of book and text.

node.text: So, it’s official (and thank you, Josh, for accidentally spilling the beans! 😂): Ron Moore (creator of Outlander and one of my creative idols) and I will co-adapt ACOTAR as a tv show for Hulu! I’m currently hard at work writing the pilot with Ron (!!!!!), and while there is SO much more news to share with you guys about bringing this series to life, it just feels so great to finally be able to talk about this! Stay tuned for more details!! 😭🥰😭 #acotar #acourtofthornsandroses #ronmoore #hulu ##RHYSSSSSSSSSS @disneytvstudios @20thtelevision

node.text: 😭😭😭 Thank you, thank you, thank you from the bottom of my heart for making this possible. I’m so phenomenally grateful for all of you—I literally don’t have words for it. This book means so much to me for so many reasons... thank you for taking this journey with me, Nesta, and Cassian. I wrote a lot of it during some of the hardest and darkest points in my life, so to reach this moment, to celebrate with you all...My heart is full to bursting. Sending you guys so much love. 💖💖💖 #acosf #acourtofsilverflames #acotar
